{"tid":308993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打同我一樣屋企都成個昆蟲王國咁？","createTime":"2017-07-04T15:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T15:44:44.000Z","uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a00e5c7235b36ec91e2d5e3e7bb216e0f5028d6","tid":308993,"uid":120540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:38:59.000Z","msg":"各位巴打養咗啲咩昆蟲係屋企？<br />\n我養咗螳螂 壁虎 蚊蚊 甲由 同 飛蛾<br />\n養到佢地肥肥白白 唔捨得走<br />\n見巴打們入到嚟 益下你地 附上寶貝寵物照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蚊蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://flic.kr/p/Wacu6y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflic.kr%2Fp%2FWacu6y&h=d9125469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n螳螂哥<br />\n<img src=\"https://flic.kr/p/V8LV5s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflic.kr%2Fp%2FV8LV5s&h=14d00c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛蛾<br />\n<img src=\"https://flic.kr/p/WacDT9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflic.kr%2Fp%2FWacDT9&h=6ed2fc71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n強叔<br />\n<img src=\"https://flic.kr/p/WacH73\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflic.kr%2Fp%2FWacH73&h=a83fd1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n𤩹虎<br />\n<img src=\"https://flic.kr/p/Wq81rB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflic.kr%2Fp%2FWq81rB&h=9aeb115c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n介紹各位巴打用捉蟲利器 咁就可以養晒咁多隻寵物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚟緊要去日本培訓 見唔到佢地 唔知會唔會好掛住呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c928f03e25fe648682d4bac6632cf3bdedadd7","tid":308993,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"死圖喎"},{"pid":"846db91ad3df9aa4fe2ced5384f216706541bdb3","tid":308993,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:44:44.000